Date Author Change

2022-01-16 Mattias Ellert <mattias dot ellert at physics dot uu dot se> - 6.24.06-3 - Backport gcc 12 fix from LLVM - Fix test failure on ppc64le and aarch64 with gcc 12
2021-12-07 Mattias Ellert <mattias dot ellert at physics dot uu dot se> - 6.24.06-2 - Fix segfaults on ppc64le when using the large code model

2021-08-27 Mattias Ellert <mattias dot ellert at physics dot uu dot se> - 6.24.04-1 - Update to 6.24.04 - Add dependency on json-devel to root-core - Disable uring in EPEL 8 (liburing is available, but uring not supported by kernel)
2021-08-04 Mattias Ellert <mattias dot ellert at physics dot uu dot se> - 6.24.02-1 - Update to 6.24.02 - ROOT now uses llvm/clang version 9 (updated from version 5) - No longer exclude arch s390x (better supported in llvm/clang 9) - Drop patches accepted upstream or previously backported - Backport some fixes that make more tests work - New subpackages: python{2,3}-distrdf, root-roofit-batchcompute - Require js-jsroot >= 6
2021-07-26 Mattias Ellert <mattias dot ellert at physics dot uu dot se> - 6.22.08-11 - Drop the memstat module for Fedora 35+ The required __malloc_hook was removed from glibc 2.33.9000-48 The memstat module is deprecated and will be removed in root 6.26
